    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I get it. \r\n\r\nFor both indexing and unindexing operations, they are all triggered by `ChainHeadEvent` event. Since you disable peer connection at all, and also your node is not synced yet, no `ChainHeadEvent` will be received. \r\n\r\nI will suggest you to remove this flag `--maxpeers 0`, let your node finish syncing(can take a few hours), then the transaction indexes will be built.",
